content:
## Breadcrumbs Types

* Location
* Path
* Attribute


### HTML Implementation

```html
    <ul class="breadcrumb">
        <li class="location"><a href="#">Shop</a></li>
        <li class="location"><a href="#">Groceries</a></li>
        <li class="location"><a href="#">Blueberries</a></li>
        <li class="location"><a href="#">Organic</a></li>
    </ul>
```




### CSS Implementation


```sass

/* Base Style */
.breadcrumb {
    padding: 8px;
}

.breadcrumb li {
    display: inline;
}

/* Location Breadcrumb */

ul.breadcrumb li.location+li.location:before {
    padding: 8px;
    content: "/\00a0";
}


/* Attribute Breadcrumb */

.breadcrumb li.attribute a {
    color: gray;
}

.breadcrumb li.attribute::after {
    content: "x";
    color: red;
    font-size: 10px;
    vertical-align: super;
}
```
